<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">它，单凭1道老坛酸菜鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每年卖出455万条鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">坚持选用水库"吊水"鲈鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鱼片像布丁一样滑，一样清甜</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">俘虏90%甜甜的广东人</p>
