<p class="ql-align-justify">这家店开在废墟里</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">独创招牌芝芝JPT奶茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">老广挚爱的3种茶底拼配，纯茶现泡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/c0aaff23bf3c4852af624acac0cf8d1a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f78e6afa2e814cb5b718ac77b9ccbab2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
