<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/2ffb4d47a2354b0cb8a55b2831bb2e63.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">嘿，今晚不加班</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">赵总请喝茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/d61c0e005a5344a8833923e431e8471e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 赵总请喝茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/c0a90a5bf8e840b6b41395d22dd3a555.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/be3bd9e184ab43a2b2cb75fa3941adb8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">石牌桥又迎来茶饮新物种『赵总请喝茶』！<strong>全新调配的茶底</strong>，把老广挚爱的茶底巨头汇集起来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>-①-</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/ 招牌芝芝JPT /</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/cb2fe2e1bef3407f884a9b0c3f421574.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">什么是JPT？纵使是茶饮界的老终结者，刚开始也是懵的~科普时间到：<strong>菊花茶+普洱茶+铁观音</strong>，三种拼配茶拼音首字母的组合，这么大的脑洞，猜对了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨茶底3重奏 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/1d4d8ee150fa428b9f69d90d08799693.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200928/ffdce2414716412faa187afea9adb241.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">看似平平无奇的茶底，实则由JPT三种茶叶冲泡混搭而成，由团队历时半年研发。<strong>菊花茶的清新、普洱茶的浓厚、铁观音的香醇</strong>，每一口都是三茶底的涌现与交织，层次感无敌了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨绵密芝士奶盖 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/cb920b0865a84cd192a1858c35e035ce.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/9b0df4978b2e4cbeb1c6611baea89e8b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/ff5c4ab8aa2c472693ece321cd169ab1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">独特的拼配茶治好了爱茶者的选择困难症,顶上绵密的奶盖给这份纯粹注入香甜气息。厚实的奶盖浮在茶水上，<strong>柔滑细腻，可盐可甜</strong>，让茶底不再空虚。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨社畜打鸡血必备 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/b90275829aca431394f56d6d60dcfd6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/119f4fd6b2ef4d348e843f53069326d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/17d3573454fc4c1980fe709ec0589015.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">给自己加油打个鸡血，我又可以了！终于可以在老板面前趾高气扬一回，当然要多炫耀一会儿！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨这些配料CP超能打 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/f3c0d7f7c562409ea02c1a80cfcecd5f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/0e4a22bf91634a6c9648c8cbdedcee2f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/a895b7d4a1c34900a76cd8046e2ca6e1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奶盖并不是JPT唯一的爱，事实上，黑糖珍珠、现做布丁、柠檬鲜果…都能成为TA的CP。<strong>JPT的浓郁、鲜奶的香醇、配料的丰富口感</strong>！别问最爱哪个，问就是基础款<strong>芝芝JPT最Dior</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>-②-</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/ 幽兰大红袍双啵奶茶 /</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/61013fe72a43413db4bfe79e1659507d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">披上金属银铠甲的大红袍双啵奶茶，也是拍照打卡必备。<strong>低调炫酷的银杯为茶饮加冕</strong>，简直就是人间《星际穿越》，不加滤镜也能凹出未来感！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/5ae84d3d683f405d98eceed89f24da41.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/d678ae5efb17455e909fc7787ac57de0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200928/50839052afdb4b70b76fc9dbff758099.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">高冷的外表也藏不住奶茶的热烈，<strong>鲜奶平衡了大红袍的微苦</strong>，Q弹爽脆的双色啵啵才是灵魂所在。一边嘬奶茶一边嚼啵啵，一整天所需的活力安排上了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/03af1b5d382f4ba99d6dda424117e651.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 试过了招牌，再从这3款入手 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>-③-</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/ 绿宝石酸奶啵啵冰 /</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/6c36e30af38c41139596c99351770e7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">墙推这杯夏日气息满满的绿宝石玫珑瓜啵啵冰。脆啵啵打底，<strong>新鲜现切的绿宝石果肉叠加</strong>，抹上酸奶挂壁，中间注入瓜瓜和绿研茶底打成的冰沙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/51cde81d44c0433fae294752ceeb5a52.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/5a9b27e6eb84492c946712e0f6983b7e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/01c120ced3b64d65b14b80f0d806ce95.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一口吸到底，香甜的玫珑瓜气息洋溢满腔，<strong>果肉清甜的汁水顺着齿缝往外渗，细腻软绵</strong>。酸奶浓浓的奶香调和瓜瓜的甜味，match度超高！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>-④-</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/ 牛油果黑糖波霸厚奶 /</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/1a445954222f408da276252134e70460.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">要想生活过得去，波霸鲜奶加点绿。带着小清新绿的<strong>“森林奶油”入口是奶油般的顺滑绵密质地</strong>。牛油果性子清淡，好在有黑糖波霸的焦香甜味互补。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200928/b51ecb30be354b808d146fff51d17a14.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200928/67a303999b7a4ba58dee1ab159c3c21c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">同时感受波霸的香甜软糯、鲜奶的香浓、牛油果的清香、厚奶盖的甜蜜，在舌尖旋转跳跃，霸道地侵袭味蕾。此时只想把<strong>爽快</strong>打在公屏！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>-⑤-</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/ 海南椰汁清补凉 /</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/3bd22e55e2464521a638554b1e977942.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">可以带着走的清补凉，<strong>一杯9层料</strong>！自制海底椰冻、银耳、椰果、玫珑瓜…光是配料就很豪华。这杯滋润的养生饮品，妈妈都来抢着喝！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/3793aae4fc4045a7b3ef934ebf66c445.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200928/dabc6aff2bce4dbc85f45f28acebed68.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">上下搅动的吸管把每种配料拌匀，<strong>裹满椰汁的清甜</strong>。工作的时候嗦一口，寡淡无味的味蕾和精神不振的脑子都在这一刻瞬间清醒！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200928/d4b78a324899476699a007d5881fc4de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 开在的废墟里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/53e1ab3e2c0a4c179f1a3d4a315f2a52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/c18dad86196f407cb5af951662df6734.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">人家都想尽办法给门店加滤镜，赵总请喝茶偏要反其道而行，把门店凿个大窟窿。<strong>假装开在废墟里的装穷风，可以说是很有个性了</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200928/ecb2742d6a30416498133c8c1ab20b5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/ef11cee670154efa88b2d9e70fcd67df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">霓虹灯、工业水泥墙、废墟墙，细节之处尽显创意和用心。在这里，<strong>随手一拍都是大片</strong>！无论是沙雕风还是靓仔照，赵总都能满足你！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200928/311f0eaa1d2d4e9695864fb57405e2d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/4afd1cb0aa5a41b99820b2d26c3e6b66.png" max-width="600" /></p>
